  "rationale": "<p>Divide every term by 2: x<sup>2</sup> + y<sup>2</sup> \u2212 4x + 6y \u2212 32 = 0. Complete the square: (x \u2212 2)<sup>2</sup> \u2212 4 + (y + 3)<sup>2</sup> \u2212 9 \u2212 32 = 0, so (x \u2212 2)<sup>2</sup> + (y + 3)<sup>2</sup> = 45. Therefore r<sup>2</sup> = 45 and r = \u221a45.</p>",
